sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Operator
    participant P as Policy Engine
    participant S as Scheduler
    participant R as Runner
    participant E as Evidence Store

    O->>P: Submit Execution Request
    P->>P: Evaluate Policy (isOrchestrationEnabled)
    alt Orchestration Disabled
        P-->>O: Direct Execution (Bypass)
    else Orchestration Enabled
        P->>P: Synthesize OrchestrationPlan
        P->>E: Emit plan_created Receipt
        P-->>O: Present Plan for Review
        O->>P: Approve Plan
        P->>E: Emit plan_approved Receipt
        P->>S: Dispatch Plan
        S->>E: Emit plan_started Receipt
        loop For each Step
            S->>P: Request Step Authorization
            P->>P: Check Trust & Approval
            alt Authorized
                P->>E: Emit decision_allowed Receipt
                S->>R: Execute Step Payload
                R->>E: Emit step_started Receipt
                R-->>S: Return Result
                S->>E: Emit step_completed Receipt
            else Denied
                P->>E: Emit decision_blocked Receipt
                S->>S: Mark Step as Failed/Skipped
            end
        end
        S->>E: Emit plan_completed Receipt
        S-->>O: Return Results + Proofpack Link
    end
